&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;“At CLEVR, we summarise the strength of our workforce in just three words: ownership, energy, and drive. With these qualities, we can enable you to level up your career and realise your potential when it comes to evolving, both personally and professionally. Are you ready to challenge yourself, learn and grow?”&lt;/em&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.linkedin.com/in/elisewesseling/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Elise Wesseling, Talent Acquisition Manager&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
